result.title: TODAY'S CONTEST PREDICTOR USING ML ON CF PERFORMANCE GRAPHS
result.content: I applied ML on my sir 1-i performance graph and find out that if he gives today's contest without my help or my friend's help (as done in the past for ratings) then his rating will decrease by 28 points. Let's see the accuracy of my ML predicitor!! If it gives a good accuracy then I will make my predictor public.
